snippet.title: Keyspace - Ludum Dare 47
snippet.description:
Puzzle platformer where you edit levels and jump on buttons, made in 72h for Ludum Dare 47.

Play the game! https://jontopielski.itch.io/keyspace

SFX / Music by Mafgar (https://twitter.com/mafgar_online)
